{"tid":1103524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【勝利醜聞】揭鄭俊英聊天室成員涉集體強姦　律師爆有10條影片","createTime":"2019-04-12T12:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T14:30:08.000Z","uid":141060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7f4e850a540c92b24ed355afbfe9f3ffc7dc5183","tid":1103524,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T12:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2671362/org/cf50269fc4352b15fb46d8994c08dd4f.jpg/_PCPF38Pp57-rHimC9FhGFv3XpVZ-qtgrbsYvK27GLw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2671362%2Forg%2Fcf50269fc4352b15fb46d8994c08dd4f.jpg%2F_PCPF38Pp57-rHimC9FhGFv3XpVZ-qtgrbsYvK27GLw&h=4b083b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國歌手鄭俊英上月被爆出在聊天群組中非法散播偷拍性愛影片，當中牽涉多位藝人包括BIGBANG前成員勝利、崔鍾訓、龍俊亨、李宗泫、Roy Kim、Eddy Kim等，牽連甚廣。雖然鄭俊英已認罪，警方也已經立案調查涉案藝人，但最新消息曝光後再度引起熱議。當初揭露事件的房律師近日接受JTBC電視台節目《Spotlight》訪問時透露，聊天群組成員涉及集體性侵，行為令人髮指。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2671540/org/e55927d90efc37133ad287cf4441111d.jpg/PtkWsgIYSO2yVBsvT7A0VvoHBsUQ796k_CE61vwhOtY?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2671540%2Forg%2Fe55927d90efc37133ad287cf4441111d.jpg%2FPtkWsgIYSO2yVBsvT7A0VvoHBsUQ796k_CE61vwhOtY%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=e9148451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據昨晚（11日）播出的JTBC節目《Spotlight》報道，節目訪問了最初舉報鄭俊英「黃金手機」的房律師，他表示聊天室內有大約10條影片，片中的受害女性在失去意識下被偷拍，懷疑加害人使用GHB（迷姦水）等藥物進行性犯罪：「有女性是在毫無意識的狀況下被拍攝影片及照片，也有推測是在強暴情況下拍攝，總共大約有10件。近日與部分受害者見了面，很多人都對當時的情況沒有記憶。」<br />\n房律師透露，聊天室內一位成員試圖性侵一名女性，但因為某些原因沒有成功，隨後另一人再度向沉睡的受害人下手。若加害者超過2人屬於「集體強姦」，經主持人追問下，房律師亦承認有兩人以上進行性侵，因而懷疑聊天室成員涉及「集體強姦」。他還指出聊天室成員完全沒有將女性看作獨立的人格體，而是當成了滿足性慾的工具，對話中甚至出現「反正都要扔掉」的字眼，相當惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n據房律師所稱，聊天室內有部分加害者被影到臉部特徵，當中包含藝人，可以推測加害者有4人，再加上在現場的人約有6人。此外，聊天群組每隔幾個月就會解散再重組一次，勝利會指示所有成員退出聊天室，之後再另開一個新的群組，而被主動刪除的記錄在通信公司的資料庫中只會保留2至3日，所以無從調查。但因為鄭俊英從沒退出原來的聊天室，聊天紀錄未被刪除，才令案件曝光。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/317429/%E5%8B%9D%E5%88%A9%E9%86%9C%E8%81%9E-%E6%8F%AD%E9%84%AD%E4%BF%8A%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%8A%E5%A4%A9%E5%AE%A4%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E6%B6%89%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E7%88%86%E6%9C%8910%E6%A2%9D%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F317429%2F%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%2588%25A9%25E9%2586%259C%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%258F%25AD%25E9%2584%25AD%25E4%25BF%258A%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%2581%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%259B%2586%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A7%25A6-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%259C%258910%25E6%25A2%259D%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8AsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=7cc05f72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/317429/%E5%8B%9D%E5%88%A9%E9%86%9C%E8%81%9E-%E6%8F%AD%E9%84%AD%E4%BF%8A%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%8A%E5%A4%A9%E5%AE%A4%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E6%B6%89%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E7%88%86%E6%9C%8910%E6%A2%9D%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87</a>"},{"pid":"6c3bad5f4d179bc907fa02b5d2782a8a84777305","tid":1103524,"uid":186997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T12:55:26.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪就係oppa嘅真面目囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b643936967f8fb670c1a468f7d7d1331165f5f3","tid":1103524,"uid":64858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T14:04:32.000Z","msg":"韓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c988d813ecc11e50c23fabf1baff3b741ecf794e","tid":1103524,"uid":122116,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T14:19:16.000Z","msg":"睇錯集體強姦個律師"},{"pid":"3f820f99cb4e2bd2597ae8a86703bd890f2bca43","tid":1103524,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c3bad5f4d179bc907fa02b5d2782a8a84777305","tid":1103524,"uid":186997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T12:55:26.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪就係oppa嘅真面目囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T14:20:47.000Z","msg":"港女會將成件事合理化"},{"pid":"1ee211aeaf3fca13e23f3c29985512b985d7156b","tid":1103524,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T14:30:08.000Z","msg":"叫到鄭俊英呢3隻字就火起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，呢條仆街"}]}